text: Mazitovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Muynaksky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 212 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 41 km from Isyangulovo, 13 km from Verkhny Muynak. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Mazitovo
